{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778905228058,"sessionID":"ses_1d102993effeo2FRSTcDHcOCWT","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"functions.write:45","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"Changes committed in PR #<NN>.\n\nThe carotid body (UBERON:0001629) has been reclassified as **part of the peripheral nervous system** (UBERON:0000010), removing the previous incorrect `part_of` relationship to the common carotid artery plus branches (UBERON:0001530). Supporting reference [PMID:32965908](https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/32965908) has been added to the definition, and the term has been linked back to this issue via a `term_tracker_item`.\n\n@dragon-ai-agent\n","filePath":"/home/runner/work/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/runner/work/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"ISSUE_COMMENTS.md","time":{"start":1778905228053,"end":1778905228057}},"id":"prt_e2f039164002ExaE3nToZK6D40","sessionID":"ses_1d102993effeo2FRSTcDHcOCWT","messageID":"msg_e2f037ff9001ak8hG5dnvW1dAC"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778905257242,"sessionID":"ses_1d102993effeo2FRSTcDHcOCWT","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"functions.write:46","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"## Summary\n\nThis PR addresses issue #3591 by correcting the anatomical classification of the **carotid body (UBERON:0001629)**. Previously, the term was incorrectly placed as `part_of` the **common carotid artery plus branches (UBERON:0001530)**, which classifies it under the cardiovascular system. Based on the literature and the functional role of the carotid body as a chemoreceptive sensory organ, it belongs in the **peripheral nervous system**.\n\n## Changes Made\n\n- **Removed incorrect relationship:**\n  - `relationship: part_of UBERON:0001530 ! common carotid artery plus branches`\n- **Added correct relationship:**\n  - `relationship: part_of UBERON:0000010 ! peripheral nervous system`\n- **Updated definition xrefs:**\n  - Added `PMID:32965908` alongside the existing `MP:0003438` to support the classification.\n- **Added term tracker metadata:**\n  - `property_value: term_tracker_item \"https://github.com/obophenotype/uberon/issues/3591\" xsd:anyURI`\n- **Added curation metadata:**\n  - `relationship: dc-contributor https://orcid.org/0000-0002-6601-2165 ! Christopher J. Mungall`\n  - `property_value: dcterms-date \"2026-05-16T00:00:00Z\" xsd:dateTime`\n\n## Rationale\n\nThe carotid body is a specialized chemoreceptive organ derived from neural crest cells and located near the bifurcation of the common carotid artery. While it sits in the adventitia of the artery, it is functionally and developmentally a component of the peripheral nervous system, not the cardiovascular system. PMID:32965908 supports this reclassification. The previous parentage was based on physical proximity rather than biological function.\n\n## Self-Review Checklist\n\n- [x] Checked out the term and reviewed existing axioms.\n- [x] Verified the target parent term (`peripheral nervous system`, UBERON:0000010) exists and is appropriate.\n- [x] Removed the incorrect `part_of` relationship.\n- [x] Added the correct `part_of` relationship.\n- [x] Added supporting literature reference (PMID:32965908).\n- [x] Added `term_tracker_item` linking back to the originating issue.\n- [x] Added curation metadata (`dc-contributor`, `dcterms-date`).\n- [x] Checked the updated stanza back into `uberon-edit.obo`.\n- [ ] `robot convert` reserialization step could not be completed because `robot` is not installed in this environment. This step is recommended before merging but was skipped here due to tooling constraints.\n\n@dragon-ai-agent\n","filePath":"/home/runner/work/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/PR_COMMENTS.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/runner/work/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/PR_COMMENTS.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"PR_COMMENTS.md","time":{"start":1778905257235,"end":1778905257240}},"id":"prt_e2f03a3b8001BIuZxwcQDO2Yqk","sessionID":"ses_1d102993effeo2FRSTcDHcOCWT","messageID":"msg_e2f037ff9001ak8hG5dnvW1dAC"}}
